00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:26,980
=Battle Through The Heaven=

18
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:29,980
=Episode 31=

19
00:01:30,950 --> 00:01:31,790
Here.

20
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:35,360
Xiao Yan.

21
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,310
Xiao Yan.

22
00:02:05,630 --> 00:02:06,470
Xiao Yan.

23
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,750
Wake up.

24
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:38,840
Xiao Yan.

25
00:02:40,110 --> 00:02:40,950
Xiao Yan.

26
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,160
Xiao Yan.

27
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:57,870
Little Fairy Doctor.

28
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,600
I got the seed of Bodhisattva.

29
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:04,000
There should still be a ray of hope.

30
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:31,750
You brat.

31
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,750
Wake up.

32
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,360
Xiao Yan.

33
00:03:37,110 --> 00:03:38,030
For the sake of everyone,

34
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,190
try your best to wake up!

35
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:41,720
Wake up.

36
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,080
Wake up.

37
00:03:59,190 --> 00:04:00,030
Go back to the Gu Clan.

38
00:04:18,350 --> 00:04:19,190
Mr. Yao.

39
00:04:20,830 --> 00:04:21,920
Why don't you say anything?

40
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,270
Am I really hopeless?

41
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:29,670
Hold on.

42
00:04:36,950 --> 00:04:38,230
I should have listened to you.

43
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:45,880
You'll be fine

44
00:04:46,550 --> 00:04:47,510
with me.

45
00:04:50,830 --> 00:04:51,670
Mr. Yao.

46
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,600
Even the seed of Bodhisattva
can't save me?

47
00:05:04,830 --> 00:05:06,720
I am going to find out anyway.

48
00:05:18,110 --> 00:05:18,950
The seed of Bodhisattva

49
00:05:19,550 --> 00:05:21,110
wraps your heart chakra.

50
00:05:22,790 --> 00:05:24,920
But your bloodline can't take
the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

51
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,160
When you run out of Dou Qi

52
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,850
and the seed of Bodhisattva
loses its root,

53
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,840
it will be fused
by the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

54
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,040
By then,

55
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,390
your heart chakra will collapse.

56
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:42,070
How many days do I have?

57
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:48,880
If it goes on day and night,

58
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:51,070
I'm afraid that at your current level
as Dou Venerate,

59
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,510
you only have ten days.

60
00:06:05,230 --> 00:06:06,830
I know what you are going to tell me.

61
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,790
I've heard it too many times.

62
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,200
But this time, no matter what you say,

63
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,890
I am going to enter the Heavenly Tomb.

64
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:18,230
Legend has it that the Heavenly Tomb
contains a source of energy.

65
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:19,600
Thousands of years ago,

66
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:21,960
Senior Xiao Xuan obtained the power
to break through the bottleneck

67
00:06:21,990 --> 00:06:23,160
in the Heavenly Tomb.

68
00:06:25,230 --> 00:06:26,070
Dad.

69
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:28,160
Only there can save Xiao Yan.

70
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:29,640
This is the last resort.

71
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:32,720
No one knows if the Heavenly Tomb

72
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:34,720
could suppress
the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

73
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,480
If not

74
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:39,390
and Purifying Lotus Demon Flame
goes berserk like last time,

75
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:40,600
what do you do?

76
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:42,160
I couldn't care less.

77
00:06:43,270 --> 00:06:45,550
If this is his destined calamity,

78
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,640
what can you change?

79
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,160
If this is a calamity,

80
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:50,390
I'll block it for him.

81
00:06:51,350 --> 00:06:52,270
If it's a debt,

82
00:06:52,790 --> 00:06:53,880
I'll pay it with myself.

83
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,950
I've seen

84
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:02,670
what Xiao Yan has done for you.

85
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:06,160
I'm not a hard-hearted man.

86
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:09,640
If I'm an ordinary father

87
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,550
and you're an ordinary daughter,

88
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:15,440
why can't I fulfill my own child?

89
00:07:17,670 --> 00:07:19,200
I owe you so much.

90
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:23,510
Why can't I do my best
to fulfill you?

91
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:30,840
Dad.

92
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:34,830
After you sent me
to the Xiao Family back then,

93
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:37,760
I got very sick.

94
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,070
I was so weak at that time

95
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:42,390
that I was about to die.

96
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:46,040
It was Xiao Yan

97
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:49,160
who channeled all of his Dou Qi to me,

98
00:07:50,350 --> 00:07:52,640
a girl with whom he had only just met.

99
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:56,110
It was Xiao Yan who saved my life.

100
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,070
I owe him.

101
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,790
I've grown up.

102
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,160
I'm not the Xun'er I was
when I was a kid

103
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:10,270
who just left home.

104
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:14,040
I've been thinking about one thing

105
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,440
all these years in the Xiao Family.

106
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,350
And I have figured it out.

107
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:26,600
If Xiao Yan dies because of me,

108
00:08:31,110 --> 00:08:32,520
I will never live alone.

109
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,000
My only concern now

110
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,400
is Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

111
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,520
If I cannot absorb it completely,

112
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,080
I will have to think of a way

113
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:54,150
to suppress it completely.

114
00:08:54,350 --> 00:08:55,280
Xiao Yan.

115
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,360
Xun'er.

116
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:57,390
Mr. Yao.

117
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:58,880
Keep this from Xun'er for me.

118
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,960
I don't want her to blame herself.

119
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,350
Xun'er, here you are.

120
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:08,760
The seed of Bodhisattva really works.

121
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:11,520
I've been fine.

122
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,160
You're just in time.

123
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,520
I have something to discuss with you.

124
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:16,520
I want to find a place,

125
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,670
preferably one with a powerful seal.

126
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:20,830
I want to take out
the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

127
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,680
We are on the same page.

128
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:24,320
Only the Heavenly Tomb
is the most suitable place

129
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:25,840
in the entire Dou Qi Continent.

130
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,120
Heavenly Tomb?

131
00:09:30,590 --> 00:09:32,000
But I don't have the power of bloodline.

132
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,390
No way.

133
00:09:37,470 --> 00:09:38,310
Absolutely not.

134
00:09:38,470 --> 00:09:41,470
If you come with me and we fail to suppress
the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame,

135
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,680
you'll get hurt too.

136
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,790
Xiao Yan.

137
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,110
Trust me, okay?

138
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,910
If the Heavenly Tomb is as rumored,

139
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:49,080
and there is a source of power,

140
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:50,790
it's worth a try.

141
00:09:54,590 --> 00:09:55,470
Xiao Yan.

142
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,030
You said before

143
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:59,030
that we can't give up hope

144
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:00,320
until the last minute.

145
00:10:00,790 --> 00:10:03,280
As long as we keep holding on,
we will see the way out.

146
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:05,910
Let me stay with you.

147
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:22,870
Dad.

148
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,920
Let's get started.

149
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:29,350
There's something else you should know
about the Heavenly Tomb.

150
00:10:31,590 --> 00:10:33,110
Countless ancestors of the Gu Clan

151
00:10:33,110 --> 00:10:35,000
and the Xiao Clan were buried there.

152
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,470
Although their physical bodies
had fallen,

153
00:10:37,470 --> 00:10:39,840
their Dou Qi was deposited
in the cave.

154
00:10:41,470 --> 00:10:42,440
Over the years,

155
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,200
many people have come here
in admiration.

156
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:47,710
They risked their lives
to steal into the Heavenly Tomb.

157
00:10:48,350 --> 00:10:50,550
The formations left there
by the ancestors of the Gu Clan

158
00:10:50,670 --> 00:10:53,200
could only be unlocked
by those with a divine bloodline.

159
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:54,360
Otherwise,

160
00:10:54,470 --> 00:10:55,310
the Heavenly Tomb

161
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:56,550
would not be a treasure,

162
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:59,640
but a grave to bury the greedy.

163
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:05,080
There is a prophecy
that has been passed down

164
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,280
to our clan about that formation.

165
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:10,230
Bear it in your mind.

166
00:11:10,710 --> 00:11:11,550
It may be of benefit to you

167
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,840
in a pinch.

168
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,080
To take,

169
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:18,080
you have to first give.

170
00:11:28,470 --> 00:11:30,790
With my blood, I pledge allegiance.

171
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,790
The Kingdom of the Spirits,
allow my mortal body.

172
00:11:34,350 --> 00:11:35,790
Heavenly Tomb, open!

173
00:11:55,110 --> 00:11:55,950
Patriarch Gu.

174
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:57,520
Do you believe in destiny?

175
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:02,000
Thousands of years ago,

176
00:12:02,030 --> 00:12:04,280
the ancestors of the Xiao Clan
fell here

177
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,830
to protect the Dou Qi Continent.

178
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,350
Thousands of years later,

179
00:12:07,550 --> 00:12:08,590
the kid of the Xiao Clan

180
00:12:08,670 --> 00:12:10,230
was sent to the same place.

181
00:12:10,910 --> 00:12:11,880
Isn't this

182
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,640
the God's will?

183
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:15,910
Since it's God's will,

184
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,040
I think

185
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:20,910
God will make
the best arrangements for him.

186
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:29,550
May the spirits of martyrs of the Gu Clan
and the Xiao Clan

187
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:32,080
bless the two children.

188
00:12:44,110 --> 00:12:44,950
Xun'er.

189
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,040
Xun'er.

190
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,590
Xiao Yan.

191
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:56,840
Xun'er.

192
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:58,280
Xun'er, where are you?

193
00:13:23,030 --> 00:13:23,870
Xiao Yan.

194
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,000
There seems to be a barrier here.

195
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:27,390
A barrier?

196
00:13:29,470 --> 00:13:31,590
I can feel your Dou Qi aura

197
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:32,880
all around me.

198
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:34,760
But I can't see you.

199
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,150
Although we are synchronized in time,

200
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:48,230
we are misplaced in space.

201
00:13:55,350 --> 00:13:56,190
Xun'er.

202
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,590
Can you see an idol?

203
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,960
Is there a mechanism inside the idol

204
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:02,520
that can break the barrier?

205
00:14:10,470 --> 00:14:11,710
Dear ancestors.

206
00:14:12,710 --> 00:14:14,840
Xiao Yan and I intruded here

207
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,670
with no offense.

208
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:19,710
I kindly ask you

209
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,230
for help.

210
00:14:47,590 --> 00:14:48,430
Is this

211
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,150
the Gu Clan's secret message?

212
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,160
Xun'er.

213
00:14:52,550 --> 00:14:53,880
Do you recognize the words on this?

214
00:14:55,110 --> 00:14:56,960
This is what my father calls a maze.

215
00:14:57,790 --> 00:15:00,670
It says here that this formation
is called the God Wood Formation,

216
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,440
set up by ancestors of my clan.

217
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:04,400
Only someone with a divine bloodline

218
00:15:04,470 --> 00:15:05,910
can unlock its mysteries.

219
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:07,940
Only by breaking through this formation

220
00:15:08,110 --> 00:15:10,030
is it possible to truly
enter the Heavenly Tomb.

221
00:15:10,590 --> 00:15:12,400
So only by breaking
the God Wood Formation

222
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:14,520
can our time and space be consistent?

223
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:21,200
But if we fail to break the formation,

224
00:15:21,880 --> 00:15:22,920
those who mistakenly enter

225
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:24,350
will suffer heaven's punishment

226
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:26,470
and be destroyed
in both form and spirit.

227
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:28,630
Xun'er.

228
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:30,670
You have the purest bloodline
of the Gu Clan,

229
00:15:31,230 --> 00:15:33,350
you can definitely break the formation.

230
00:15:34,790 --> 00:15:35,630
I got it.

231
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,970
Then I'll give it a try
with my power of bloodline.

232
00:15:44,030 --> 00:15:45,150
What a powerful energy.

233
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,280
No.

234
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,880
Purifying Lotus Demon Flame
is coming out.

235
00:16:02,350 --> 00:16:03,230
Xiao Yan.

236
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:07,720
Xiao Yan.

237
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:09,640
How are you?

238
00:16:28,350 --> 00:16:29,190
Xun'er.

239
00:16:29,790 --> 00:16:30,630
I am fine.

240
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:33,900
I have the seed of Bodhisattva
and I still have time.

241
00:16:44,910 --> 00:16:45,750
Xun'er.

242
00:16:46,790 --> 00:16:48,440
What you have to do now is simple.

243
00:16:49,710 --> 00:16:51,150
Find the right door.

244
00:17:23,310 --> 00:17:24,150
Why?

245
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:25,950
Why can't I sense anything?

246
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:34,000
Xun'er.

247
00:17:35,310 --> 00:17:36,880
You've always had a good perception.

248
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,240
Do you remember?

249
00:17:41,190 --> 00:17:43,760
When we were at Jia Nan Academy
and Wutan City,

250
00:17:44,760 --> 00:17:46,110
you could always sense the aura
of Dou Qi

251
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:48,590
before anyone else.

252
00:17:51,430 --> 00:17:52,430
I didn't know that.

253
00:17:53,710 --> 00:17:55,280
This is your power of bloodline.

254
00:18:06,070 --> 00:18:06,910
Xun'er.

255
00:18:08,190 --> 00:18:09,040
Don't think about me.

256
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:11,430
Don't worry.

257
00:18:12,470 --> 00:18:14,150
Don't think
about the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

258
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:15,480
I can do it.

259
00:18:17,800 --> 00:18:18,680
So can you.

260
00:18:28,760 --> 00:18:29,600
(No way.)

261
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:32,350
(If this goes on,
the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame will explode.)

262
00:18:33,230 --> 00:18:34,590
(If the formation isn't broken)

263
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:36,400
(and our time and space are not consistent,)

264
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:37,840
(I might as well)

265
00:18:38,190 --> 00:18:40,040
(let it explode here.)

266
00:18:40,310 --> 00:18:42,110
(That way Xun'er will be fine.)

267
00:18:47,520 --> 00:18:48,360
Xun'er.

268
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:49,670
Listen to me.

269
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:54,350
The energy here is way too powerful.

270
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:59,040
The seed of Bodhisattva can no longer
contain the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

271
00:18:59,040 --> 00:18:59,880
My heart chakra

272
00:19:00,430 --> 00:19:01,400
may soon...

273
00:19:06,430 --> 00:19:07,270
Xun'er.

274
00:19:08,070 --> 00:19:09,160
I don't have time for this.

275
00:19:10,520 --> 00:19:13,160
I want the Purifying Lotus
Demon Flame to explode here.

276
00:19:13,350 --> 00:19:14,190
